trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse" /> class is generated by the server when a severe error occurs.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse" /> 類別 (Class) 由伺服器在發生嚴重錯誤時產生。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse.Controls" /> property is not applicable to a DSML <errorResponse>.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse.Controls" /> 屬性不適用於 DSML <errorResponse>。

trans-unit.source: Not applicable to a DSML <errorResponse>.
trans-unit.target: 不適用於 DSML <errorResponse>。

trans-unit.source: This property is not valid for a DSML error response.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性對 DSML 錯誤回應無效。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse.Detail" /> property contains the contents of the <detail> element of the errorResponse, if any.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse.Detail" /> 屬性包含 errorResponse 之 <detail> 項目的內容 (如果有)。

trans-unit.source: The contents of the <detail> element of the errorResponse, if any.
trans-unit.target: 內容<詳細>errorResponse，如果有任何項目。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlErrorResponse.Type" /> 屬性包含指定伺服器傳回之錯誤回應類型 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ErrorResponseCategory" /> 的值。

trans-unit.source: A value of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ErrorResponseCategory" /> that specifies the type of the error response returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ErrorResponseCategory" /> 的值，指定伺服器傳回之錯誤回應的類型。

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the "type" attribute of the \<errorResponse> element.
trans-unit.target: 此屬性會對應至"type"屬性的\<errorResponse > 項目。
